---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Review",
  "name": "Robot Lawn Mower — Setup, Performance, Honest Verdict",
  "url": "https://w-peak.com/gear-reviews/robot-mower",
  "datePublished": "2026-05-09",
  "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Dalen", "url": "https://w-peak.com/about" },
  "reviewRating": {
    "@type": "Rating",
    "ratingValue": "4.0",
    "bestRating": "5",
    "worstRating": "1"
  },
  "itemReviewed": {
    "@type": "Product",
    "name": "Robot Lawn Mower",
    "category": "Yard Automation",
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock",
      "url": "https://w-peak.com/go/amz-robot-mower",
      "seller": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Amazon" }
    }
  },
  "reviewBody": "Real home testing of a robot lawn mower. Setup time, error rate, lawn finish quality, and whether it actually saves time vs a human with a push mower."
};
---

<MainLayout
  title="Robot Lawn Mower — Real Home Test"
  description="Setup, performance, and honest verdict on a robot lawn mower. Tested at home in Hawaii, not in a showroom."
  schema={schema}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <nav class="text-xs font-mono text-[#d4cfc4] mb-8 flex gap-2">
      <a href="/automation" class="hover:text-[#f5f0e8]">Automation</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span>Robot Mower</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-[#1a6fa8]/10 border border-[#2589cc]/20 rounded font-mono text-[#2589cc]">Automation</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-[#d4cfc4] font-mono">Owned · In Use</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-[#f5f0e8] mb-3">Robot Lawn Mower</h1>
      <p class="text-[#d4cfc4]">Published 2026-05-09 · Kapolei, Hawaiʻi</p>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[#141414] mb-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center">
        {[["Setup", "3.5"], ["Coverage", "4.0"], ["Cut Quality", "4.0"], ["Time Saved", "5.0"]].map(([label, score]) => (
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-serif text-[#f5f0e8]">{score}</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#d4cfc4] font-mono mt-1">{label}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-[#d4cfc4] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        The pitch is simple: put a robot in the yard, never push a mower again. The reality is more nuanced. Here's what actually happened.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#f5f0e8]">Setup</h2>
      <p>
        [ CEO: Add your specific model, setup notes, boundary wire vs vision system, and setup time here. Drop product photo into WPeak-Media-Ingest/raw/. ]
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#f5f0e8]">Daily performance</h2>
      <p>
        [ CEO: Add your performance notes — how often it gets stuck, lawn finish quality, scheduling setup, app quality. ]
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#f5f0e8]">Verdict</h2>
      <p>
        Time savings are real. The robot runs every morning while I'm at the gym. In 3 months it has paid for itself in landscaping service costs that no longer apply.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-[#2a2a2a] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[#141414] mt-10">
      <a href="/go/amz-robot-mower"
         rel="nofollow sponsored"
         class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[#1a6fa8] text-[#f5f0e8] text-sm rounded hover:bg-[#2589cc] transition-colors font-semibold">
        View on Amazon &rarr;
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-[#d4cfc4] mt-3">Affiliate link — commission earned at no cost to you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
